s/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-4-1529x2048.jpg 1529w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-4-150x201.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd there’s another reason why the soup feels a bit heartier than you’d think: \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003ewe’re mashing some of the beans!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor years you guys have been telling me that this is one of your favorite ways to thicken soups. I don’t do a full puree, but I do mash one whole can to add some creaminess and texture. It’s awesome! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"cozy white bean kale soup\" width=\"1688\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/white-bean-kale-soup/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Cozy White Bean \u0026amp; Greens Soup.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-scaled.jpg 1688w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-728x949.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-768x1001.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-1179x1536.jpg 1179w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-1571x2048.jpg 1571w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-5-150x195.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1688px) 100vw, 1688px\" dat