tps://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-scaled.jpg 1725w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-728x929.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-768x980.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-1204x1536.jpg 1204w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-1606x2048.jpg 1606w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1725px) 100vw, 1725px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201725%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-scaled.jpg 1725w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-728x929.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-768x980.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-1204x1536.jpg 1204w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-1606x2048.jpg 1606w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-150x191.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShortly before serving, I toss in the spinach and kale. It cooks down almost instantly. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis is where I taste things, maybe add some extra parmesan, more salt or pepper, even some crushed red pepper flakes! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnnnnd it’s time to serve. YUM.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"cozy white bean kale soup\" width=\"1790\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/white-bean-kale-soup/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Cozy White Bean \u0026amp; Greens Soup.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-scaled.jpg 1790w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-728x895.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-768x944.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-1250x1536.jpg 1250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-1666x2048.jpg 1666w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-150x184.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1790px) 100vw, 1790px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201790%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-scaled.jpg 1790w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-728x895.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-768x944.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-1250x1536.jpg 1250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-1666x2048.jpg 1666w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-150x184.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-10-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt’s a great meal prep soup because there is no pasta to soak the broth up. And at the same time, you can totally add in some pasta! A tiny cut, or even some quinoa. Couscous, rice, anything you love! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOf course, you could also throw in some rotisserie chicken, cooked sausage or more. It’s a lovely base for any kind of soup. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMake it your own!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"cozy white bean kale soup\" width=\"1718\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/white-bean-kale-soup/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Cozy White Bean \u0026amp; Greens Soup.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-scaled.jpg 1718w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-728x932.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-768x983.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-1199x1536.jpg 1199w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-1599x2048.jpg 1599w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-9-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1718px) 100vw, 1718px\"