eans-and-greens-soup-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-8-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eCozy White Bean \u0026amp; Greens Soup\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"97894\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e35\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e45\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis white bean kale soup is a winter staple. It\u0026#39;s hearty and rich from the parmesan broth and mashed beans, loaded with vegetables and tons of flavor. And it\u0026#39;s good for you too! Love love love.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97894\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/sweet-onions-2lb-bag-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77789463?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003esweet onion,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ediced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ediced carrots\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/celery-hearts-16oz-2ct-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-78873570?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ediced celery\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic cloves,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eminced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eparmesan rind\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(14 ounce)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e cans white beans, \u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003edrained and rinsed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echicken or vegetable stock\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ehead kale,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ewash and torn from the stems, coarsely chopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-baby-spinach-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54555537?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efresh baby spinach\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/sartori-sarvecchio-parmesan-cheese-wedge-5-3oz/-/A-47562259?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eparmesan cheese,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/mccormick-pepper-red-crushed-4-62oz/-/A-79502634?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ecrushed red pepper,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97894\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97894-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat the olive oil in a large stock pot over medium heat.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97894-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd the onions, carrots, celery and garlic with a few big pinches of salt and pepper. Stir and cook, until the veggies soften, about 6 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97894-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd in the parmesan rind, 2 cans of the beans and the stock. Bring the mixture to a boil then reduce it to a simmer. Cover and simmer for 20 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97894-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn those 20 minutes, mash the remaining can of beans. I do this with a fork or a potato masher right into a bowl. I just give them a coarse mash and add them right to the soup!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97894-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter 20 minutes, stir in the kale and spinach. Food for 5 to 10 minutes more. Taste and season with more salt and pepper as needed.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97894-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eServe with lots of parmesan on top, as well as crushed red pepper.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSoup\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"cozy white bean kale soup\" width=\"1750\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/white-bean-kale-soup/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Cozy White Bean \u0026amp; Greens Soup.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-scaled.jpg 1750w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-728x915.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-768x966.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-1222x1536.jpg 1222w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-1629x2048.jpg 1629w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-150x189.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1750px) 100vw, 1750px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201750%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-scaled.jpg 1750w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-728x915.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-768x966.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-1222x1536.jpg 1222w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-1629x2048.jpg 1629w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-150x189.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/white-beans-and-greens-soup-11-scal